  <條文>
    <條號>Article 34</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[In a profit-seeking enterprise operated by sole proprietorship or partnership, the loan borrowed by the proprietor or the partner shall all be considered dealings of capital owners, and shall not be listed as interest.
]]></條文內容>
