    <條號>Article 42</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of income stated in Subparagraph 2, Article 36 of the Act refers to the amount of income approved by the governing tax office, where the donated amount that shall be listed as expenses or losses shall be adjusted according to the approved amount of income in accordance with statutory limits.
]]></條文內容>
