    <條號>Article 89-1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Where the various incomes subject to withholding prescribed in Paragraph 1, Article 88 of the Act are incomes earned in kind, in the form of valuable securities or in foreign currencies, Paragraph 2, Article 14 of the Act shall apply upon computation.
]]></條文內容>
